      "content": "Subject: Our Sincere Apologies and a Special Offer for Your Breville Barista Pro Espresso Machine\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to extend our sincerest apologies for the delay in delivering your Breville Barista Pro espresso machine. We understand how important this purchase was to you, and we deeply regret any inconvenience this delay may have caused.\n\nOur team has been tirelessly working to resolve the glitch in our warehouse shipping system. We have identified the root cause and have taken steps to ensure that such an issue does not occur again. As a token of our appreciation for your patience and understanding, we would like to offer you a 15% discount on your next order with us. This discount will automatically be applied to your account.\n\nWe value your business and are committed to providing you with the best possible service. Should you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to reach out to us.\n\nThank you for your understanding and continued support.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Your Contact Information]",
